Package com.ca.codesv.sdk

Provides classes of SDK of CodeSV.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Bundler
    Bundler defines the capabilities of the engine for bundling observed requests and responses during playback.
    ClientRequest
    Client request.
    ClientRequestHandler
    Client request handler.
    Connection
    Connection marker interface.
    Interceptor
    Connection interceptor responsible for registering ClientRequestHandler with endpoint connection.
    Protocol<T extends Connection,R extends ResponseBuilder>
    Protocol implementation class responsible for providing interceptor and request/response transformers.
    RawBody
    Interface representing raw body of Request and Response.
    RepositoryConfig  
    RequestTransformer
    Transforms Request to RawRequest.
    ResponseBuilder
    ResponseBuilder specifies the minimum necessary for the protocol to provide for the framework to be able to build responses for the protocol.
    ResponseBuilderProvider<R extends ResponseBuilder>
    ResponseBuilderProvider specifies the ability to provide a ResponseBuilder on demand.
    ResponseTransformer
    Transforms Response to RawResponse.

    RawResponse
    Raw response message containing meta and request body.
    Request
    Common request message.
    Response
    Common response message.
